573
00:40:37,980 --> 00:40:39,710
Especially you guys.

574
00:40:40,550 --> 00:40:41,550
You guys.

575
00:40:41,950 --> 00:40:44,390
You representative delinquents.

576
00:40:45,650 --> 00:40:46,760
Jung Hee!

577
00:40:49,290 --> 00:40:52,090
Study hard for this, got it?

578
00:40:52,460 --> 00:40:55,660
Darn it. He's always picking on us.

579
00:41:40,080 --> 00:41:41,480
Did something happen?

580
00:41:43,040 --> 00:41:44,880
Is it because of Jin?

581
00:41:47,950 --> 00:41:50,750
(Kim's Pharmacy)

582
00:41:50,750 --> 00:41:51,750
Excuse me.

583
00:41:54,760 --> 00:41:55,920
I noticed before...

584
00:41:56,490 --> 00:41:58,260
that your kitchen ceiling was leaking.

585
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:03,270
Is something wrong?

586
00:42:04,400 --> 00:42:05,800
My dad...

587
00:42:07,070 --> 00:42:08,800
hasn't come home for several days.

588
00:42:10,410 --> 00:42:12,110
He hasn't even called.

589
00:42:23,290 --> 00:42:24,690
Please help me.

590
00:42:28,990 --> 00:42:30,390
How long has it been?

591
00:42:30,390 --> 00:42:31,760
It's been a few days.

592
00:42:32,460 --> 00:42:35,560
He's never not come home
without calling before.

593
00:42:38,830 --> 00:42:39,900
Hae Joo!

594
00:42:44,370 --> 00:42:47,140
What is it? What did you say to her?

595
00:42:47,340 --> 00:42:49,580
- It's not like that.
- What did you say?

596
00:42:49,580 --> 00:42:52,080
- Jung Hee.
- I'll look into it.

597
00:42:53,080 --> 00:42:54,680
What was it? Where are you going?

598
00:42:54,680 --> 00:42:57,350
It's not like that. I
asked him for a favor.

599
00:42:57,790 --> 00:42:58,850
What?

600
00:43:02,560 --> 00:43:04,130
I need to go home.

601
00:43:04,330 --> 00:43:05,430
See you tomorrow.

602
00:43:06,360 --> 00:43:07,430
Hae Joo.

603
00:43:10,600 --> 00:43:11,870
Be careful...

604
00:43:12,930 --> 00:43:14,070
of Young Choon.

605
00:43:14,800 --> 00:43:18,170
You shouldn't talk to him and stuff.

606
00:43:20,810 --> 00:43:22,140
Thanks.

607
00:43:22,940 --> 00:43:24,150
But...

608
00:43:25,210 --> 00:43:27,650
he isn't such a bad person.

609
00:44:20,240 --> 00:44:21,300
Dad.

610
00:44:23,570 --> 00:44:24,810
Kyung Soo.

611
00:44:31,850 --> 00:44:33,720
- Sir.
- Hey.

612
00:44:34,520 --> 00:44:37,150
Have you seen this man?

613
00:44:38,390 --> 00:44:39,590
No, I haven't.

614
00:44:44,960 --> 00:44:46,960
Please let me know.

615
00:44:47,460 --> 00:44:48,960
I'll be in touch.

616
00:45:08,720 --> 00:45:11,050
I wonder if something's
going on with Hae Joo.

617
00:45:14,090 --> 00:45:15,320
Jung Hee.

618
00:45:17,890 --> 00:45:19,090
A study room?

619
00:45:20,000 --> 00:45:21,100
Quiet.

620
00:45:22,330 --> 00:45:24,600
Mom got you a pass to a study room?

621
00:45:25,670 --> 00:45:27,200
- Mom!
- Jung Hee.

622
00:45:27,400 --> 00:45:30,810
Go to the study room in my place.

623
00:45:31,070 --> 00:45:32,310
I'll give you my pass.

624
00:45:32,310 --> 00:45:35,040
No! I want my own.

625
00:45:35,040 --> 00:45:36,880
I'll give you this too.

626
00:45:37,010 --> 00:45:40,180
I saved my allowance to buy something.

627
00:45:40,280 --> 00:45:43,750
You get to study thanks
to me and make money.

628
00:45:43,890 --> 00:45:46,120
This is your lucky day.

629
00:45:53,090 --> 00:45:56,230
- Darn it. Mom!
- I'll give you my piggy.

630
00:45:57,170 --> 00:45:58,230
You know...

631
00:45:58,870 --> 00:46:01,240
I have a big piggy living
in my room, right?

632
00:46:01,770 --> 00:46:03,000
I...

633
00:46:03,240 --> 00:46:05,610
saved up all my birthday money, allowance,

634
00:46:05,610 --> 00:46:08,040
everything since I was a baby.

635
00:46:08,710 --> 00:46:10,210
I'll give it to you whole.

636
00:46:10,810 --> 00:46:13,420
They'll call home if I don't show up.

637
00:46:14,120 --> 00:46:15,280
Jung Hee.

638
00:46:16,650 --> 00:46:18,520
- Where is it?
- Will you go?

639
00:46:30,130 --> 00:46:31,600
(Boys' Study Room)

640
00:46:33,240 --> 00:46:35,000
(Girls' Study Room)

641
00:46:37,970 --> 00:46:41,540
Bong Soo. Of all the things...

642
00:46:43,380 --> 00:46:45,880
But then again, I get to study...

643
00:46:46,350 --> 00:46:47,550
and make money.

644
00:46:49,420 --> 00:46:51,390
It's just one week.

645
00:47:02,630 --> 00:47:03,730
Go in.

646
00:47:21,820 --> 00:47:23,020
Stinky.

647
00:47:26,620 --> 00:47:29,020
Okay, Jung Hee. You can do it.

648
00:47:29,520 --> 00:47:32,160
Let's try getting into a special class.

649
00:47:39,170 --> 00:47:40,200
What?

650
00:47:40,770 --> 00:47:42,340
You won't go to the study room?

651
00:47:46,310 --> 00:47:47,580
This is a great opportunity.

652
00:47:47,640 --> 00:47:50,710
I'll say I'm studying, and
party all night instead.

653
00:47:52,110 --> 00:47:54,820
Bong Soo. Have you lost your mind?

654
00:47:55,020 --> 00:47:56,120
That's right.

655
00:47:56,180 --> 00:47:59,620
Don't you know they'll
call home if you don't go?

656
00:47:59,620 --> 00:48:00,890
I know that.

657
00:48:01,060 --> 00:48:04,530
That's why the second
Lee Bong Soo is there.

658
00:48:05,960 --> 00:48:09,400
Otherwise known as Lee Jung Hee.

659
00:48:10,700 --> 00:48:11,800
What?

660
00:48:13,400 --> 00:48:14,540
It's full?

661
00:48:14,700 --> 00:48:17,910
It's exam time, so it's full.

662
00:48:20,410 --> 00:48:22,440
Then is Bong...

663
00:48:22,880 --> 00:48:26,410
No, no. I can't risk getting her caught.

664
00:48:29,890 --> 00:48:33,820
May I go in briefly to talk to a friend?

665
00:48:38,990 --> 00:48:41,360
(No outsiders)

666
00:49:04,720 --> 00:49:07,590
She'll come out eventually.

667
00:49:19,370 --> 00:49:22,400
Jung Hee's studying so hard.

668
00:49:54,900 --> 00:49:57,070
So? Did you find out?

669
00:49:57,570 --> 00:49:58,710
Well...

670
00:50:02,410 --> 00:50:04,310
I looked everywhere...

671
00:50:11,150 --> 00:50:12,520
I'll look more.

672
00:50:25,100 --> 00:50:26,430
Why were you out here?

673
00:50:27,470 --> 00:50:28,540
Go inside.

674
00:50:32,340 --> 00:50:33,680
I was too scared.

675
00:50:40,050 --> 00:50:41,450
You should go.

676
00:50:42,020 --> 00:50:43,950
Eng Cho must be waiting.

677
00:50:46,420 --> 00:50:48,720
Eng Cho is sleeping.

678
00:50:49,420 --> 00:50:50,990
What if...

679
00:50:51,990 --> 00:50:55,260
something happened to my dad?

680
00:51:01,240 --> 00:51:02,640
Don't be afraid.

681
00:51:04,810 --> 00:51:06,070
I'm here.

682
00:51:37,740 --> 00:51:39,240
What's going on?

683
00:51:39,910 --> 00:51:41,310
Jin is...

684
00:51:42,980 --> 00:51:44,980
No.

685
00:52:40,170 --> 00:52:44,910
(Rainbow Study Room)

686
00:52:46,610 --> 00:52:48,110
Is it curfew already?

687
00:53:16,070 --> 00:53:17,140
Well,

688
00:53:17,870 --> 00:53:19,870
I have no choice.

689
00:53:20,710 --> 00:53:22,010
Does this mean...

690
00:53:22,610 --> 00:53:24,250
I'll be spending...

691
00:53:24,810 --> 00:53:27,420
my first night with Jin tonight?

692
00:53:36,790 --> 00:53:39,860
Jung Hee. You stupid girl.

693
00:53:40,660 --> 00:53:41,930
Are you that happy?

694
00:53:46,670 --> 00:53:48,800
Yes, I am.

695
00:53:49,400 --> 00:53:50,910
I can't help it.

696
00:53:55,440 --> 00:53:56,780
Jin.

697
00:54:43,930 --> 00:54:46,390
I wish time would stop.

698
00:54:58,370 --> 00:55:03,680
(Rainbow Study Room)

699
00:55:11,120 --> 00:55:12,150
2:40am...

700
00:57:00,330 --> 00:57:02,060
Why did it have to be next to Jin?

701
00:57:36,430 --> 00:57:38,630
Jung Hee. Don't worry.

702
00:57:39,230 --> 00:57:41,770
I'll protect you tonight.

703
00:57:42,840 --> 00:57:45,310
(Rainbow Study Room)

704
00:58:16,200 --> 00:58:20,440
(Rainbow Study Room)

705
00:58:25,550 --> 00:58:27,720
I feel so stiff.

706
00:58:27,720 --> 00:58:31,220
Uhn Joo. She says she never studies.

707
00:58:31,220 --> 00:58:32,750
Where should we eat?

708
00:58:32,750 --> 00:58:34,720
They'll get the wrong idea if they see me.

709
00:58:35,260 --> 00:58:37,360
What? What about him?

710
00:58:38,060 --> 00:58:40,800
- Whatever.
- Aren't you sleepy?

711
00:58:41,630 --> 00:58:42,760
Seriously.

712
00:58:42,760 --> 00:58:44,070
Stop it.

713
00:58:44,630 --> 00:58:46,870
Gosh, I'm so tired.

714
00:58:47,170 --> 00:58:49,840
Let's go home.

715
00:58:51,710 --> 00:58:54,080
Darn it. What the...

716
00:58:59,680 --> 00:59:01,380
I have to go home.

717
00:59:04,620 --> 00:59:08,760
"Potential. Having the
capacity to become..."

718
00:59:08,760 --> 00:59:09,930
Leap.

719
00:59:10,730 --> 00:59:13,060
To jump, spring.

720
00:59:14,330 --> 00:59:15,730
Adorable.

721
00:59:17,370 --> 00:59:18,570
Adorable.

722
00:59:19,570 --> 00:59:20,670
Adorable?

723
00:59:22,470 --> 00:59:23,740
Adorable?

724
00:59:24,340 --> 00:59:25,840
Adorable.

725
00:59:32,350 --> 00:59:35,120
Cute. Lovable.

726
00:59:36,380 --> 00:59:37,450
Pardon?

727
00:59:39,250 --> 00:59:40,360
Adorable.

728
00:59:41,120 --> 00:59:43,530
Cute. Lovable.

729
00:59:49,360 --> 00:59:50,370
Do you know...

730
00:59:51,200 --> 00:59:54,140
that you're kind of cute?

731
00:59:55,540 --> 00:59:58,310
What was that?

732
01:00:00,110 --> 01:00:04,310
I don't know English sentences yet.

733
01:00:10,950 --> 01:00:12,220
I mean you're cute.

734
01:00:13,990 --> 01:00:15,090
You. Jung Hee.

735
01:00:24,970 --> 01:00:26,530
Son Jin.
